<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361775>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Phylogenetic tree generated from ML analysis based on a combined LSU, ITS, mtSSU, and SSU sequence data. The bootstrap support (bs) values of ML equal to or greater than 75%, and Bayesian posterior probabilities (PP) equal to or greater than 0.95 are given near the nodes as ML/PP, respectively. Onygena corvina (CBS 281.48) and Trichocoma paradoxa CBS (78893-IFO 30659) were used as outgroup taxa. The newly generated sequences are indicated in black bold. “T” denotes ex-type strain." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361777>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2.Sclerococcumpseudobactrodesmium(HKAS128890,holotype).a,bColonies onthenaturalsubstrate surface.cSporodochium. d–k Conidiophores, conidiogenous cells, and conidia. l–n Conidia. o Germinating conidium. p, q Colonies on PDA from above and below. r Umbonate colony surface on PDA from the side. Scale bars: c = 50 µm, d–f, h–k = 20 µm, g, l–o = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361777/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

